<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background: #667eea; color: white !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to DevTrack!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
      <p>Welcome to DevTrack! We're excited to help you track your development sessions and boost your productivity.</p>
      <p>Get started by:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Creating your first project</li>
        <li>Starting a development session</li>
        <li>Viewing your analytics dashboard</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="{{frontendUrl}}" class="button">Get Started</a>
      <p>Happy coding!</p>
      <p>The DevTrack Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>You received this email because you signed up for DevTrack.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
